<h2 style="color: #dc3545;"><%= @document_type %> Parse Failed</h2>

<p>Your uploaded <strong><%= @document_type %></strong> could not be processed and has been marked <strong>failed</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>Document:</strong> <%= @document.name %><br>
<strong>File:</strong> <%= @document.try(:original_filename) || "—" %><br>
<strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @error_message %></p>

<p>The original file has been retained so you can review it. To resolve:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Sign in to SPARC</li>
  <li>Open the document to review the failure details</li>
  <li>Correct the file and re-upload to retry</li>
</ol>

<% if @app_url.present? %>
  <p><%= link_to "Open SPARC", @app_url %></p>
<% end %>
